Package ie.gmit.dip

Class Settings

java.lang.Object
ie.gmit.dip.Settings
public class Settings
extends java.lang.Object
Settings class that creates an object that stores all the parameters for processing a word cloud (input file name, word count, input text source and number of threads to map word frequency).
